WEBVTT

00:04.200 --> 00:07.901
Alright, locking it up.
Who needs a ride home?

00:10.623 --> 00:12.201
Come on, who needs a ride home?

00:12.333 --> 00:15.453
l guess we're all sober enough
to drive ourselves tonight.

00:15.670 --> 00:18.457
Looks like you get to go
straight home for a change.

00:18.590 --> 00:21.923
l've never driven straight home.
l wouldn't know how to do it.

00:22.052 --> 00:26.630
- OK, Coach. You can take me.
- What a prince.

00:26.765 --> 00:29.386
- Thanks, l owe you one.
- Any time.

00:29.518 --> 00:31.261
Goodnight now.

00:31.394 --> 00:32.889
Drop me off at Kenmore Square.

00:33.021 --> 00:35.939
l can catch a cab
to take me back here to my car.

